---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="testimonials">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Trusted by Industry Leaders
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        See how BuildNow is transforming material financing across Saudi Arabia
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Ahmed Al-Saud</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">CEO, Al Riyadh Contractors</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"BuildNow transformed how we handle large projects. Their flexible payment solutions allowed us to take on 40% more contracts last year. The platform's efficiency in processing material orders is outstanding."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar-1.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Khalid Al-Rashid</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Operations Director, Jeddah Building Materials</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"As a supplier, the immediate payment feature has revolutionized our cash flow. We've seen a 60% increase in order volume since partnering with BuildNow, while eliminating payment collection headaches."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Mohammed Al-Qahtani</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Managing Director, Dammam Trading Co.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"The ability to maintain a full inventory without capital constraints has been game-changing. Our customers appreciate the flexible payment terms, and we've seen a 75% reduction in lost sales opportunities."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar-3.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Faisal Al-Harbi</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Project Manager, Makkah Developers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"BuildNow's platform helped us complete our latest residential project 3 months ahead of schedule. The streamlined material procurement and payment process eliminated traditional delays."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar-4.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Abdullah Al-Otaibi</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Finance Director, Saudi Steel Works</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"As a manufacturer, BuildNow's credit solutions have enabled us to optimize production cycles and meet growing demand. Our revenue has grown by 50% since implementing their financing solutions."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="/images/avatars/avatar-5.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Saad Al-Ghamdi</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Owner, Medina Construction Supplies</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"The risk-free payment guarantee has allowed us to focus on growing our business instead of chasing payments. BuildNow's platform has become essential to our operations."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>